							singleType="STRING";
							value="All on-site personnel are to acknowledge the following: " \n " " \n "At approximately 02:40 local time, a critical containment failure occurred within the lower sectors of the Blackwater Research Complex. Automated lockdown procedures were enacted immediately. Since that time, command authority has been disrupted and interdepartmental communication remains unstable." \n "All Facilities have been locked down at this time, all personnel are recommended to locate their nearest armoury and defend until Security Services can resecure the facility";
